  ('dietitian-moex-11194', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '血紅素的正常值，約為：   16 g/100 mL   16 mg/100 mL   16 mg/mL   16 g/mL （請接背面） 全一張 九十三年第二次專門職業及技術人員高等暨普通考試醫事人員、 中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試試題 類    科： 營養師', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2e2b6219eaf", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11195', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '凝血機轉完成後之善後工作是：thrombin由凝血作用變成反作用，因為thrombin可與thrombomodulin作用而引起下列何種 蛋白質之活化？   protein A   protein B   protein C   protein F', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2e2b6219eaf", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
